OL,3,CPoisoned buzzard sees pheasant
OL,4,Cbreeding farm and director fined #40k
OL,6,FA pheasant breeding farm in Devon has
OL,7,Fbeen fined more than #40,000 following
OL,8,Fthe discovery of a poisoned buzzard.
OL,10,FPolice found a stash of illegal
OL,11,Fchemicals when they raided Ashley Game
OL,12,FFarm at Chulmleigh in 2021.
OL,14,FAt Exeter Magistrates Court, company
OL,15,Fdirector Christopher Hodgson was also
OL,16,Ffined more than #1,500.
OL,18,FBoth the company and Hodgson admitted
OL,19,Fa string of pesticide offences.
