OL,3,CPoisoned buzzard sees pheasant
OL,4,Cbreeding farm and director fined #40k
OL,6,FIn October 2020, a member of the
OL,7,Fpublic discovered a dead Buzzard, a
OL,8,Fprotected species under the Wildlife
OL,9,Fand Countryside Act 1981, lying on top
OL,10,Fof a pheasant carcass by a pheasant
OL,11,Frelease pen, near Hollocombe in Devon,
OL,12,Fand reported it to Devon and Cornwall
OL,13,FPolice.
OL,15,FThe two birds and a second dead
OL,16,Fpheasant found nearby were sent to the
OL,17,FGovernment's Wildlife Incident
OL,18,FInvestigation Scheme for toxicology
OL,19,Ftests.
