OL,3,CPoisoned buzzard sees pheasant
OL,4,Cbreeding farm and director fined #40k
OL,6,FMeat found in the Buzzard's beak and
OL,7,Fboth pheasant carcasses tested
OL,8,Fpositive for the insecticide
OL,9,FCarbofuran.
OL,11,FDevon and Cornwall police, supported
OL,12,Fby the National Wildlife Crime Unit,
OL,13,FNatural England and the RSPB, searched
OL,14,FAshley Game Farm.
OL,16,FThey found significant amounts of
OL,17,Fprohibited and unauthorised pesticides
OL,18,Fand veterinary medicines.
