OL,3,CPoisoned buzzard sees pheasant
OL,4,Cbreeding farm and director fined #40k
OL,6,FA forensic search of two vehicles
OL,7,Fdetected positive traces of the banned
OL,8,Fpesticide Carbofuran, the same banned
OL,9,Fpesticide which had been found on the
OL,10,Fpheasant carcasses and which had
OL,11,Fcaused the Buzzard's death.
OL,13,FCarbofuran has been banned in the UK
OL,14,Fsince 2001 because of its high
OL,15,Ftoxicity and associated risks.
OL,17,FMark Thomas, the RSPB's Head of
OL,18,FInvestigations said: "Yet again the
OL,19,Fdiscovery of a dead bird of prey and
OL,20,Fpoisoned bait leads to the detection
OL,21,Fof lethal banned poisons.
