OL,6,F"As past cases have demonstrated these
OL,7,Fchemicals are extremely hazardous to
OL,8,Four wildlife and environment, but also
OL,9,Fpose a considerable risk to members of
OL,10,Fthe public and domestic animals."
OL,12,FHoward Jones, RSPB Senior
OL,13,FInvestigations Officer said: "The fact
OL,14,Fthat Carbofuran is still being found
OL,15,F20 years after it was banned shows the
OL,16,Flack of reform, as the law stipulates,
OL,17,Fbeing shown by some within the
OL,18,Fgamebird industry."
