OL,6,FJenny Mashford from Devon and Cornwall
OL,7,FPolice said: "This incident was
OL,8,Fbrought to the police's attention
OL,9,Fthanks to a member of the public who
OL,10,Fidentified the poisoned raptor.
OL,12,F"It is a very positive outcome in our
OL,13,Ffight against wildlife crime, of which
OL,14,Fbird of prey crime is a national
OL,15,Fwildlife crime priority."
